OL,3,CIndia rejects UK parliament report on
OL,4,Ctransnational repression
OL,6,FWords by Sanjay Jha, ITV News
OL,7,FJournalist
OL,9,FIndia has launched a blistering
OL,10,Fcounterattack against a UK
OL,11,Fparliamentary report that accused it
OL,12,Fof waging "transnational repression"
OL,13,Fon British soil and misusing global
OL,14,Fpolicing tools like INTERPOL to
OL,15,Fsilence political dissidents.
OL,17,FIn a strongly worded statement on
OL,18,FIndia's foreign ministry denounced the
OL,19,Fallegations as "baseless,"
OL,20,F"politically motivated," and "drawn
OL,21,Ffrom dubious and discredited sources."
