OL,6,F"The deliberate reliance on unverified
OL,7,Finputs from proscribed entities with a
OL,8,Flong record of anti-India hostility
OL,9,Fcalls into question the credibility
OL,10,Fand objectivity of the entire report,"
OL,11,Fsaid MEA spokesperson Randhir Jaiswal,
OL,12,Fdismissing the claims as an
OL,13,Forchestrated smear.
