OL,3,CIndia rejects UK parliament report on
OL,4,Ctransnational repression
OL,6,FThe rare diplomatic rebuke was
OL,7,Ftriggered by the release of a hard-
OL,8,Fhitting report titled "Transnational
OL,9,FRepression in the UK" on July 30 by
OL,10,Fthe UK Parliament's Joint Committee on
OL,11,FHuman Rights ` a powerful cross-party
OL,12,Fbody comprising lawmakers from both
OL,13,Fthe House of Commons and House of
OL,14,FLords.
