OL,3,CIndia rejects UK parliament report on
OL,4,Ctransnational repression
OL,6,FThe report accuses multiple foreign
OL,7,Fgovernments of targeting exiled
OL,8,Fdissidents, activists, and journalists
OL,9,Fwho have sought refuge in the UK,
OL,10,Fcreating what it describes as a
OL,11,F"chilling effect" on diaspora
OL,12,Fcommunities.
OL,14,FIndia was named among 12 countries,
OL,15,Fincluding China, Russia, Iran, and
OL,16,FSaudi Arabia, allegedly involved in
OL,17,Fsuch practices.
