OL,6,FThese groups allege that Indian
OL,7,Fauthorities have sought to weaponise
OL,8,Finternational policing tools to harass
OL,9,Fand intimidate diaspora voices,
OL,10,Fespecially those supporting the
OL,11,FKhalistan separatist movement ` a
OL,12,Fclaim India has long dismissed as
OL,13,Fmisinformation propagated by extremist
OL,14,Felements.
