OL,3,CIndia rejects UK parliament report on
OL,4,Ctransnational repression
OL,6,FWhile the report has reignited debate
OL,7,Fwithin Britain over how to protect
OL,8,Fresidents from foreign interference,
OL,9,FIndia's sharp reaction signals a
OL,10,Fpotential diplomatic flashpoint `
OL,11,Fparticularly amid already sensitive
OL,12,Fties following the killing of Sikh
OL,13,Fseparatist Hardeep Singh Nijjar in
OL,14,FCanada last year, which also raised
OL,15,Fquestions around cross-border
OL,16,Fintelligence operations.
